net.nemerosa.ontrack.extension.api

Interface BuildDiffExtension

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ActionExtension, Extension
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GitChangeLogExtension, SVNChangeLogExtension

    public interface BuildDiffExtension
extends ActionExtension
    This extension allows to an action on the selection of two builds for the same project.

    The ActionExtension.getAction() method must point to a REST endpoint that accepts a BuildDiffRequest as a GET parameter and returns a BuildDiff as a decorated response.
